name: 2016 Olio Quattrociocchi Rosemary
description: The special organic aromatic oils from Olio Quattrociocchi are a must-try. Specially fused with rosemary during the crushing of the olives, this oil is made exclusively from olives grown on their organic farm in Alatri from the Itrana, Moraiolo, Leccino and Frantoio varieties. Try this oil with roasted chicken, lamb and potatoes, or drizzled over grilled vegetables.
